  <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
    I’m Albert, a junior developer based in Trondheim, originally from 
    Barcelona. After more than 10 years working in transport and logistics, 
    I decided to transition into software development driven by a long-standing 
    interest in technology and problem-solving.
  </p>

