    connecting them to reliable APIs.
  </p>

  <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
    My background in logistics and customs has given me strong professional 
    maturity, ownership and attention to detail — qualities I now apply to 
    writing maintainable code and collaborating in technical teams.
  </p>

  <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
